 that supplies tiled vector data"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"text","text":"Mapbox Vector Tile"},{"type":"text","text":" format"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to be shown on the map. The location of and metadata about the tiles are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"defined either by an option dictionary or by an external file that conforms to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TileJSON specification"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A vector tile source is added to an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object along with one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" objects. A vector style layer defines the appearance of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"any content supplied by the vector tile source."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnvectortilesource","title":"MLNVectorTileSource","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorTileSource","kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionbuffer","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSNumber"},{"type":"text","text":" object containing an integer; specifies the size of the tile"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"buffer on each side. A value of 0 produces no buffer. A value of 512 produces a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"buffer as wide as the tile itself. Larger values produce fewer rendering"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"artifacts near tile edges and slower performance. The default value is 128."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOptionMinimumZoomLevel":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionminimumzoomlevel","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSNumber"},{"type":"text","text":" object containing an integer; specifies the minimum zoom level at"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which to create vector tiles. The default value is 0."}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionMinimumZoomLevel","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionMinimumZoomLevel"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionMinimumZoomLevel","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSource":{"title":"MLNShapeSource","fragments":[{"text":"MLNShapeSource","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesource","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shown on the map. The shapes may be instances of "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or they may be defined by local or external"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"GeoJSON"},{"type":"text","text":" code. A shape source is added to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object along with an "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the shape source. You"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can update a shape source by setting its "},{"code":"shape","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"URL","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeCollection":{"title":"MLNShapeCollection","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeCollection"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeCollection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeCollection","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of zero or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"distinct but related shapes that are instances of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":". The constituent"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shapes can be a mixture of different kinds of shapes."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapecollection","role":"symbol"}}}